<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #4f5ef1;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .message-sm {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-top: 50px;
      }
      .message-sm > h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 25px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .course-info {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px 0px;
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(206, 197, 197, 0.1);
        color: #000;
      }
      .course-info > h4 {
        color: #23bd70;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .first-td {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #0000006c;
        font-size: 16px;
        padding: 5px 0px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .second-td {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #000000af;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      td {
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      td.col-2 {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: left;
        padding: 0px;
      }
      .table-row {
        width: 70%;
        display: block;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 10px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 100px;
        color: #fff;
      }
      .footer > p > a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #fff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="message-sm">
        <h1>Đơn hàng MindX của bạn đã được xác nhận!</h1>
        <p>Và chúng tôi cũng phấn khích như bạn vậy.</p>
      </div>

      <br /><br />

      <div class="course-info">
        <h4>Đây là những gì bạn đã đặt hàng:</h4>

        <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f">
          <tr>
            <td>Đơn hàng#: <%= order._id %></td>
            <td>Ngày đặt: <%= order.date %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block">
          <tr>
            <td class="first-td">Mục</td>
            <td class="first-td">Số lượng</td>
            <td class="first-td">Trị giá</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block">
          <tr>
            <td class="second-td"><%= order.name %></td>
            <td class="second-td">1</td>
            <td class="second-td"><%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #00000029">
          <tr>
            <td class="col-2">Tổng phụ:</td>
            <td class="col-2"><%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <table class="table-row" style="margin-top: -20px">
          <tr>
            <td class="col-2">Tổng cộng:</td>
            <td class="col-2"><%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Nếu bạn có bất kỳ câu hỏi nào, vui lòng liên hệ:
          <a href="mailto:maitrang.071003@gmail.com">maitrang.071003@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>&copy; 2026 MindX. Bảo lưu mọi quyền.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
